---
import LegalPage from '../layouts/LegalPage.astro';
---
<LegalPage
  title="Terms of Service - CrushCue"
  description="CrushCue's terms of service: acceptable use, subscriptions, AI-generated content, and your responsibilities."
  footerLinks={[
    { href: '/privacy', label: 'Privacy Policy' },
    { href: '/support', label: 'Support' },
  ]}
>
  <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
  <p class="updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>

  <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
  <p>
    By using CrushCue, you agree to these Terms of Service. If you do not agree,
    please do not use the app.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Age Requirement</h2>
  <p>
    You must be at least 18 years old to use CrushCue. By using the app,
    you confirm that you are 18 years of age or older.
  </p>

  <h2>3. About CrushCue</h2>
  <p>
    CrushCue provides AI-generated suggestions for dating, texting, and social
    communication. The app is designed to help users think through messages and
    conversations in a more confident and natural way.
  </p>

  <h2>4. AI-Generated Content</h2>
  <p>
    CrushCue uses artificial intelligence to generate responses and suggestions.
    AI-generated content may be inaccurate, inappropriate, incomplete, or unsuitable
    for your specific situation. You are responsible for reviewing and deciding
    whether to use any suggestion.
  </p>

  <h2>5. No Guaranteed Results</h2>
  <p>
    CrushCue does not guarantee any outcome in dating, relationships, conversations,
    or social interactions. Suggestions are provided for informational and
    entertainment purposes only.
  </p>

  <h2>6. User Responsibility</h2>
  <p>
    You are fully responsible for the messages you send, the decisions you make,
    and the way you use the app. CrushCue is not responsible for any consequences,
    misunderstandings, emotional distress, lost relationships, or other outcomes
    resulting from use of the app.
  </p>

  <h2>7. Acceptable Use</h2>
  <p>
    You agree not to use CrushCue to harass, threaten, manipulate, deceive,
    impersonate others, abuse, stalk, exploit, or harm others. You also agree not
    to use the app for illegal, hateful, sexually exploitative, or otherwise
    inappropriate behavior.
  </p>

  <h2>8. Subscriptions and Payments</h2>
  <p>
    CrushCue may offer paid subscription plans such as monthly or yearly Pro access.
    Subscription prices, features, and limits may vary by region and may change over time.
  </p>
  <p>
    Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled before the end of the current
    billing period. Payment and renewal are handled by the App Store or Google Play,
    depending on where you purchased the subscription.
  </p>

  <h2>9. Cancellations and Refunds</h2>
  <p>
    You can manage or cancel your subscription through your App Store or Google Play
    account settings. Refund requests are handled by Apple or Google according to
    their own refund policies. CrushCue does not directly process store refunds.
  </p>

  <h2>10. Account Suspension</h2>
  <p>
    We may suspend or terminate access to CrushCue if we believe you have violated
    these Terms, abused the service, attempted to bypass usage limits, or used the
    app in a harmful or unlawful way.
  </p>

  <h2>11. Account Deletion</h2>
  <p>
    You can delete your account at any time from within the app.
  </p>
  <p>
    Deleting your account will permanently and irreversibly remove your profile,
    preferences, message history, usage data, and all associated information,
    unless retention is required by law.
  </p>

  <h2>12. Service Availability</h2>
  <p>
    We aim to keep CrushCue available and reliable, but we do not guarantee
    uninterrupted access. The app may be unavailable due to maintenance,
    technical issues, high traffic, third-party outages, or other reasons.
  </p>

  <h2>13. Limitation of Liability</h2>
  <p>
    To the fullest extent permitted by law, CrushCue is not liable for indirect,
    incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, or for any loss
    resulting from your use of or inability to use the app.
  </p>

  <h2>14. Changes to These Terms</h2>
  <p>
    We may update these Terms from time to time. Continued use of CrushCue after
    changes are posted means you accept the updated Terms.
  </p>

  <h2>15. Contact</h2>
  <p>
    If you have questions about these Terms, contact us at:<br /><br />
    <span class="contact">contact@crushcue.app</span>
  </p>
</LegalPage>

<style>
  h1 {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    font-size: 36px;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 32px 0 10px;
    font-size: 19px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  p {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .updated {
    color: var(--dim);
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }

  .contact {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 30px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 17px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  }
</style>
